Conversion:
Rewrite for use as universal exchange backend.
1) Outbound TX
  A) Query a out-tx-db for:
    request timestamp, currency, amount, tx-sender, tx-recipient
  B) Update out-tx-db with txid, processed flag

2) Inbound TX
  Write to in-tx-db:
    tx timestamp, currency, txid, tx-amount, tx-to, tx-from

